Dear Customer,

To ensure the smooth collection of your shipment by EXPRESS on January 30, 2024, between 10:00 and 15:00, please follow these instructions:

children.text: To re-book a collection if missed.
Please email Innovatech at innovatech.returns.uk@express.com and quote    reference:{$data.data.shipping_information.customer_instructions.reference_number}..
If you have a dedicated packing box or are using your own, do not seal it before the EXPRESS driver arrives.
When the driver arrives, both you and the driver will sign a security sticker. This sticker will then be used to seal the box or flyer.
Ensure the driver signs your copy of the label as proof of collection.
Batteries that are damaged or defective are prohibited from air transport and will not be accepted by EXPRESS.
